><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.evangelion.co.jp/news/shineva2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.evangelion.co.jp%2Fnews%2Fshineva2%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDe2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=91b1dcca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.evangelion.co.jp/news/shineva2/</a>"},{"pid":"3ae4614e3a7b5e047ceb0e7c9c7aece7ad5cc39c","tid":2360471,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOmbRJa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOmbRJa.jpg&h=1247f94d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"339e30cbcb595d1200112750d2a99c602b15f36a","tid":2360471,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:25:25.000Z","msg":"放心<br />\n到時又會有d因素唔上映話要改依樣果樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}